  <name>Commander Genius</name>
    
  <summary>A Game Engine for "Commander Keen"</summary>
  
  <supports>
    <control>pointing</control>
    <control>keyboard</control>
    <control>gamepad</control>
  </supports>

    <description>
  <p>
 Commander-Genius aka CloneKeenPlus is an engine which interprets
 Commander Keen 1-6, Dreams and Cosmos the Cosmic Adventure.
    </p>
  <p>
  But there is more: How about four player coop, VGA graphics, remastered music and
  many great mods to apply. There even exists the unoffical trilogy that was planned back then
  (Keen 7-9). Eventhough that trilogy was never released, it got picked up by fans. 
  With an integrated CG game store you can download every free game with one click and
  start playing.
  </p>
  <p>
 For registered Keen games you need the game data of the games
 in order to play them. Check the Readme file for more information on that.
 Episode 2, 3, 5 and 6 are registered versions which can be
 purchased by 3D Realms, Apogee, GOG or bought by someone else.
 If you still have the old games of the registered version,
 then copy those into a reachable directory and give it a try.
   </p>  
  </description>
  
